metadata.name: AccountStatusesCleanupService #call when the account has posted several old statuses when called repeatedly with a budget of 2 reports 2 then 1 deleted statuses

sql_query.sql: SELECT MAX(id) FROM (SELECT "statuses"."id" FROM "statuses" WHERE "statuses"."deleted_at" IS NULL AND "statuses"."account_id" = 111361448932414106 AND "statuses"."id" BETWEEN 0 AND 111282176589824000 ORDER BY "statuses"."id" ASC LIMIT 5000) t
